 * - Construct from components using [UtcOffset] (hours, minutes, seconds).
 * - Parse strings using [parse] (ISO-8601 formats) or create custom [Format]s.
 * - Obtain from [TimeZone.offsetAt] for a particular [Instant].
 *
 * When to use:
 * - To format or parse offsets in text (e.g., "+02:00").
 * - To construct [FixedOffsetTimeZone] via [asTimeZone] when a fixed offset (without DST) is required.
 *
 * ISO-8601:
 * - [toString] uses extended ISO-8601 with `Z` for zero.
 * - [Formats.ISO], [Formats.ISO_BASIC], and [Formats.FOUR_DIGITS] provide predefined formats.
 *
